title: Green Bay Packers, Real Super Bowl Contenders, Baker Mayfield, Kawhi Leonard
itunes:title: Green Bay Packers, Real Super Bowl Contenders, Baker Mayfield, Kawhi Leonard
description:
Colin talks about why he doesn't believe the Packers are a significant threat to win the Super Bowl and gives his list of contenders as the playoffs grow near. He responds to Baker Mayfield after the Browns QB clapped back at him on Monday night and weighs in on the report that Kawhi Leonard's uncle had some questionable demands this past offseason.

Guests include Reggie Bush, Bucky Brooks and Peter King
